column1: What is jenkins?;Jenkins is a continuous integration and continuous delivery tool that is used to coordinate the development efforts of a large software project. It is an open-source automation server used to build
column2: test and deploy software projects. Jenkins automates software development and delivery processes and helps automate tasks related to building
